Create the following dotnet user-secrets for PMT.Api:
    Authentication:Google:ClientId          # Exactly what it says
    App:Secret                              # The secret key of your app. 32byte minimum
    App:Issuer                              # eg. https://www.api.example.com
    App:Audience                            # eg https://www.example.com
    App:AdminEmail                          # Used for seeding the db, creating initial user. eg firstname.lastname@gmail.com. Must be a gmail address!
    App:CORS:Origin                         # Location of front-end, eg mathieu.eylenbosch@github.io/pmt-angular

Create the following anguler environment variables in PMT.client/environments/environment.ts and PMT.client/environment/environment.development.ts:
    GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID: "put_your_google_client_id_here",
    ENDPOINT_URI: "https://api.localhost:5015"
